The Ohme Home Pro and Easee One sit at similar price points, but they take fundamentally different approaches to home EV charging. One bets everything on smart software and tariff integration. The other leads with gorgeous hardware and multi-charger flexibility.

Both are excellent chargers. But which one should you actually buy? We've put them head-to-head across every category that matters for UK buyers in 2026.

